<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>800</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>yào bǎ nǐ de zhēn ài chuán biàn 迦南800</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wú lùn wǒ men wǎng nà lǐ qù, qiú nǐ yǔ wǒ men tóng zài.
 qiú nǐ bù jiào wǒ men yù jiàn shì tàn, bǎo hù wǒ men yī lù píng ān.
 shēn zhī nǐ fēng fù wú xiàn de ēn diǎn, zú gòu wǒ men měi tiān yòng.
 yù jiàn wēi xiǎn nǐ bì gěi wǒ men kāi lù. suǒ yǐ wǒ men zǒng bù sàng dǎn.
 cóng méi yǒu huái yí guò nǐ de xìn shí, shí guāng yǐ jīng gěi wǒ dá àn.
 wú lùn shí dài rú hé biàn qiān, wéi yǒu nǐ de cí ài yǒng bù biàn.
 sī xiǎng nǐ de ēn diǎn, xīn zhōng hé děng shòu gǎn. tiān de zuò zhǐ hǎi shuǐ zuò mò, xiě yě xiě bù wán.
 wǒ men jīn tiān yào cóng zhè lǐ qǐ háng, yào bǎ nǐ de zhēn ài chuán biàn</lyrics>
</song>